<br>
I gfluxed the mage to the top of one of the buildings then he CoH the rest of us.  With lev we ran to the invis ramp.  Then we proceeded from there.  That way we didn't have to deal with all the reavers inside the building.  We went all the way to the back and just kept killing everything near that last little building untill the wraith finally popped.  Was kind of boring but eventually he popped and I was able to charm and do my turn in.<br>
<br>
