<br>
I fought my way to the gazebos near the reaver building and then i looked straight up.  You will see the building floating above you.  From here you should see some mobs wandering above you.<br>
<br>
Target one of the mobs above and cast a bind sight spell (one that lets you see through someone elses perspective) then look for the mob that stands right in front of the door to the building.  I had a 65 wizzy with me so he nuked 'em down for me untill WoJ pop'd but i'm sure you could nuke them on your own.  They dont really aggro they just kinda stand there.<br>
<br>
Once the Wraith of Jaxion spawns what I did was I put myself on auto follow on the wizzy and I casted shifted sight on WoJ.  Then I feared him and he runs back toward the invis bridge back towards the arena. (make sure that you have cleared all the mobs that have repop'd since you last passed through here before pulling WoJ)  The wizzy started the run to the invis bridge while i auto followed him ( i was still sight bound) and then when we got to the arena I casted fear again because my first wore off about there. Then I charmed him when he was on the invisable bride and told him to back off.  He came right down next to me and I was able to give him the Ruby.  Then i just ran for the zone.  Didnt really bother killing him.  <br>
<br>
If you break your sight bound you will not be able to cast on the WoJ cuz it says &quot;you cannot see your target&quot;  just FYI !<br>
<br>
So that is how I did it.  I hope that this helps someone. GL! <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.forgeoflegends.com/members/Luzza/prismatta.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=683364">Be enticed by my gear!</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFF0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=emredrum>Emredrum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#CC3300>(9/22/03 11:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=65.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Wraith of Jaxion strategy pls</span><hr size=1> I love it Prisamatta...Where ever there is a will, there is a way.  Gratz. Inspiring!<br>
